<h1>Introduction</h1>

<p>The Bear Sorceress Enchantress is one of the most Unique builds in the entire game. By taking advantage of the @@@D2Beast@@@ Runeword the Sorceress is able to turn into a Bear while Enchanting herself for large amounts of Fire Damage and using @@@D2Dream@@@ Runewords to gain Lightning Damage further increased by her @@@D2LightningMastery@@@. Overall it is a very expensive build but when fully built out is a ton of fun and can kill even the strongest of bosses in Uber Tristram.</p>

<h1>Quick Reference</h1>

<h2>Skill Build</h2>

<p>The following section shows the core skills for the Bear Sorceress. For a detailed breakdown of all core and optional skills as well as the recommended order for allocating skill points, refer to the Skills section of this guide.</p>

<ol>
<li>1 point to all prerequisites</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Enchant@@@ - Main Damage boost Skill, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Warmth@@@ - Synergy for @@@D2Enchant@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2FireMastery@@@ - Added Damage for @@@D2Enchant@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2LightningMastery@@@ - Added Lightning Damage, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2Teleport@@@ - invest immediately at level 18, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2StaticField@@@ - invested at level 6, let the Resistancest of your plus skills increase its range, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2FrozenArmor@@@ - Useful for defensive purposes, required</li>
</ol>

